snippet.title: Black Legend - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Black Legend - Dark Turn-Based Strategy combined with free level exploration set in a 17th century fantasy world.
Coming to PC, Switch, Xbox series X and PS5 early 2021!

Find out more: https://www.blacklegendgame.com

Follow the game on social media: 
https://www.facebook.com/warcavegames
https://twitter.com/warcavegames
https://store.steampowered.com/publisher/Warcave
